3731pub(crate) fn composition_table_astral(c1: char, c2: char) -> Option<char> {
3732    match (c1, c2) {
3733        ('\u{11099}', '\u{110BA}') => Some('\u{1109A}'),
3734        ('\u{1109B}', '\u{110BA}') => Some('\u{1109C}'),
3735        ('\u{110A5}', '\u{110BA}') => Some('\u{110AB}'),
3736        ('\u{11131}', '\u{11127}') => Some('\u{1112E}'),
3737        ('\u{11132}', '\u{11127}') => Some('\u{1112F}'),
3738        ('\u{11347}', '\u{1133E}') => Some('\u{1134B}'),
3739        ('\u{11347}', '\u{11357}') => Some('\u{1134C}'),
3740        ('\u{114B9}', '\u{114B0}') => Some('\u{114BC}'),
3741        ('\u{114B9}', '\u{114BA}') => Some('\u{114BB}'),
3742        ('\u{114B9}', '\u{114BD}') => Some('\u{114BE}'),
3743        ('\u{115B8}', '\u{115AF}') => Some('\u{115BA}'),
3744        ('\u{115B9}', '\u{115AF}') => Some('\u{115BB}'),
3745        ('\u{11935}', '\u{11930}') => Some('\u{11938}'),
3746        _ => None,
3747    }
3748}

35662#[inline]
35663pub fn stream_safe_leading_nonstarters(c: char) -> usize {
35664    match c {
35665        '\u{0340}' => 1,
35666        '\u{0341}' => 1,
35667        '\u{0343}' => 1,
35668        '\u{0344}' => 2,
35669        '\u{0F73}' => 2,
35670        '\u{0F75}' => 2,
35671        '\u{0F81}' => 2,
35672        '\u{FF9E}' => 1,
35673        '\u{FF9F}' => 1,
35674        _ => 0,
35675    }
35676}
